io.cdap.http.internal

Class HttpResourceModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.cdap.http.internal.HttpResourceModel

  • public final class HttpResourceModel
extends Object
    HttpResourceModel contains information needed to handle Http call for a given path. Used as a destination in PatternPathRouterWithGroups to route URI paths to right Http end points.
